<!doctype html>
<html lang="en" class="h-100">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Uplead Forex Academy</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.0-beta1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
      body {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        scroll-behavior: smooth;
      }
      
      h2 {
        color: hsl(218, 41%, 15%);
      }

      h5 {
        color: #ad1fff;
      }

      /* Hero Section */
      .hero-section {
        position: relative;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .hero-section img {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
      }

      .hero-text {
        padding: 2rem;
      }

      .logout-btn {
        position: absolute;
        top: 10px;
        right: 10px;
      }

      /* Services Cards */
      .card {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff, #f0f8ff);
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        padding: 20px;
        margin-top: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
      }

      .card:hover {
        transform: scale(1.05);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 15px hsl(218, 81%, 75%);
      }

      /* Animations for Cards */
      .card {
        animation: slideInUp 0.7s ease-in-out;
      }

      @keyframes slideInUp {
        from {
          opacity: 0;
          transform: translateY(30px);
        }
        to {
          opacity: 1;
          transform: translateY(0);
        }
      }

      /*Contact us*/
      #contact-us {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        padding: 50px 20px;
    }
    form {
        background: white;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    form button {
        background-color: hsl(218, 41%, 45%);
        border: none;
        color: white;
    }
    form button:hover {
        background-color: hsl(218, 41%, 35%);
    }
    

      /* Footer */
      footer p {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: #6c757d;
      }

      footer a {
        color: #ad1fff;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      footer a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header class="container py-3">
      <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light">
        <a class="navbar-brand" href="#" style="color: hsl(219, 75%, 52%)">Uplead Forex Academy</a>
        <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav">
          <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
        </button>
        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
          <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
            <li class="nav-item">
              <form action="/logout?_method=DELETE" method="POST">
                <button class="btn btn-dark logout-btn" type="submit">Logout</button>
              </form>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <main class="container">
      <section class="hero-section">
        <img src="https://exc-prodp.s3.eu-west-2.amazonaws.com/uploads/what-is-forex-trading-and-how-does-it-work-og.png" alt="Uplead ForexAcademy Image">
        <div class="hero-text">
          <h1 style="color: hsl(219, 75%, 52%)">Hi <%= name %>, Welcome to <span >Uplead Forex Academy</span> </h1>
          <p class="lead">Learn profitable trading strategies and achieve financial freedom.</p>
          <a href="#learn-more" class="btn btn-primary">Learn More</a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="learn-more" class="mt-5">
        <h2 style="color: hsl(219, 75%, 52%)">Why Choose Us?</h2>
        <p>We are the leading forex trading academy, renowned for being trustworthy and reliable. At Upleade Forex Academy, we prioritize people's needs above everything else, ensuring tailored support for every learner. With over 500 students who have successfully transitioned into professional traders, we continue to empower individuals to achieve financial independence through expert guidance and structured learning.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="mt-5">
        <h2 style="color: hsl(219, 75%, 52%)""> Our Services</h2>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Forex Trading Course</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Master the fundamentals of forex trading, including the best technical and fundamental analysis using the price action model. Gain the confidence to navigate global currency markets like a pro.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Mentorship</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Gain exclusive insights and personalized guidance from industry experts. Elevate your trading skills, learn advanced strategies, and build a robust trading plan tailored to your goals..</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Copy Trading with NeolinFx</h5>
                <p class="card-text">For those who don't have the time to learn trading, you can copy trades from me and enjoy the profits from my expert analysis. Let my strategies work for you!.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Trading Bots and Strategies</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Automate your trading with custom-built bots for MT5, with mobile versions coming soon. Optimize performance, minimize risks, and seize opportunities effortlessly.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section id="contact-us" class="mt-5">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="text-center mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
            <p class="text-center">We'd love to hear from you! Reach out to us with any questions or inquiries.</p>
            <div class="row">
                <!-- Contact Form -->
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <form action="/submit-contact" method="POST" class="p-4 shadow-lg rounded">
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label for="name" class="form-label">Full Name</label>
                            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="name" name="name" placeholder="Enter your full name" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label for="email" class="form-label">Email Address</label>
                            <input type="email" class="form-control" id="email" name="email" placeholder="Enter your email address" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label for="message" class="form-label">Your Message</label>
                            <textarea class="form-control" id="message" name="message" rows="5" placeholder="Write your message here" required></textarea>
                        </div>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary w-100">Send Message</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
                <!-- Contact Details -->
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="p-4">
                        <h4>Get in Touch</h4>
                        <p><strong>Email:</strong> support@upleadforexacademy.com</p>
                        <p><strong>Phone:</strong> +123 456 7890</p>
                        <p><strong>Address:</strong> 123 Avenue, Harare, Zimbabwe</p>
                        <h5>Follow Us:</h5>
                        <p>
                            <a href="#" class="me-2"><i class="bi bi-facebook"></i> Facebook</a>
                            <a href="#" class="me-2"><i class="bi bi-twitter"></i> Twitter</a>
                            <a href="#"><i class="bi bi-linkedin"></i> LinkedIn</a>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    </main>

    <footer class="container text-center py-3">
      <p>&copy; 2025 Uplead Forex Academy. All rights reserved. Developed by <a href="http://www.elfo.co.zw" target="_blank">Elfo</a>.</p>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.0-beta1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
